{"tid":2210349,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中國的發明 - 顏純鈎","createTime":"2020-09-20T10:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T12:05:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"239bf6aa68b0ebc3ce9587eb0a12d7d242425d39","tid":2210349,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:40:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200920/JD7VMR6EUVGENOKEJL2KBL4P2E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200920%2FJD7VMR6EUVGENOKEJL2KBL4P2E%2F&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2OmrVsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=e51dcdfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200920%2FJD7VMR6EUVGENOKEJL2KBL4P2E%2F&h=f6f83bf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200920/JD7VMR6EUVGENOKEJL2KBL4P2E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中國的發明 - 顏純鈎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sK3uHll-oHbd9l0IXDM0LpB0Uuc=/700x394/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZIF57NGYXFCUJHUFNLF4X2AOO4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsK3uHll-oHbd9l0IXDM0LpB0Uuc%3D%2F700x394%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZIF57NGYXFCUJHUFNLF4X2AOO4.jpeg&h=46530862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前寫過一篇短文，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n張教授引用的數據是：。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n這500多年裏，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中國在過去五百年，沒有一項創新發明可以載入史冊，意味着我們對人類的貢獻幾乎為零。<br />\n<br />\n張教授也以人口比例來說明問題，學術界普遍認為創新與人口比例的關係，是指數的關係，不是簡單的等比例的關係。中國的人口是美國的4倍，是日本的10倍，英國的20倍，瑞士的165倍，按照知識創造的指數縮放規則，中國的發明創造應是美國的5.6倍，日本的17.8倍，英國的42.3倍，瑞士的591倍，但實際情況是，近500年來，中國在發明創造方面，對世界的貢獻幾乎為零。<br />\n<br />\n我們連瑞士都不如。瑞士人至少發明了手術鉗﹑電子助聽器﹑安全帶﹑整形技術、液晶顯示器等等，印刷錢幣用的防偽油墨也是瑞士發明的。<br />\n<br />\n張教授認為問題出在我們的體制和制度，創造力依賴的是自由，思想的自由和行動的自由，中國體制的特點就是扼殺人的自由。<br />\n<br />\n當然，。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"0507eb90789248961e68b511b5bdb2e2839ab79b","tid":2210349,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7650df63d1fafe0a4efd780663f38cdf0f46ffb9","tid":2210349,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國人讀書係用嚟入大公司 入政府機關做 做特權階層"},{"pid":"888bfa4e321d1e74a0d65eda874fd37e319a29ef","tid":2210349,"uid":79562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:49:00.000Z","msg":"2020年總有支那人吹奏四大發明架<br />\n<br />\n明明係科技樹最基礎幾項 唔同地方唔同文明都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ef7f89f4237a6420d5a29a2aa8768cd52ebc60","tid":2210349,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:50:51.000Z","msg":"乜嘢信用評分，人臉識別，支那寶囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa262a9d13d40cfa6e6c208e78f811148ff7ecf4","tid":2210349,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:55:08.000Z","msg":"支那賤畜=地球癌"},{"pid":"bb04e0e64c9b41a072e054aa5e04df4a104b4c60","tid":2210349,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T11:04:28.000Z","msg":"偷呃拐騙技術領先世界500年"},{"pid":"6a9be51c4f28c77fd8e17718c6119431db2c1b97","tid":2210349,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T12:05:13.000Z","msg":"歐洲發明民主制度係令佢地領先既最大關鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}